# Summary Reports Rule

## When This Rule Applies

This rule **automatically applies** when:
- User says "summarize", "create summary", "summary of"
- The AI creates summary documentation of work completed
- Creating executive summaries, project summaries, or session summaries
- Documenting completed sprints, phases, or milestones

---

## Core Principle

**All summary reports must be saved in a consistent location with standardized naming and structure.** This ensures:
- Easy reference for stakeholders
- Clear documentation of progress
- Trackable project history
- Consistent executive communication

---

## Storage Location

### Required Location

**All summary reports MUST be saved to:**
```
docs/_reports/summaries/
```

### Folder Structure

```
docs/
└── _reports/
    └── summaries/
        ├── README.md                           # Index of all summaries
        ├── project_summary_2025-12-09.md       # Project overview
        ├── sprint_summary_2025-12-09.md        # Sprint completion
        ├── session_summary_2025-12-09.md       # Work session summary
        ├── feature_summary_2025-12-09_auth.md  # Feature completion
        ├── migration_summary_2025-12-01.md     # Migration summary
        └── release_summary_2025-11-15_v2.md    # Release summary
```

---

## Naming Convention

### Required Format

```
{summary_type}_summary_{YYYY-MM-DD}[_context].md
```

**Components:**
- `{summary_type}` - Type of summary in `snake_case`
- `_summary_` - Literal string (required)
- `{YYYY-MM-DD}` - Date of summary
- `[_context]` - Optional context (e.g., version, feature, sprint)

### Summary Type Examples

| Summary Type | Filename |
|--------------|----------|
| Project | `project_summary_2025-12-09.md` |
| Sprint | `sprint_summary_2025-12-09_sprint14.md` |
| Session | `session_summary_2025-12-09.md` |
| Feature | `feature_summary_2025-12-09_user_auth.md` |
| Release | `release_summary_2025-12-09_v2_0.md` |
| Migration | `migration_summary_2025-12-09_db.md` |
| Phase | `phase_summary_2025-12-09_phase2.md` |
| Weekly | `weekly_summary_2025-12-09.md` |
| Monthly | `monthly_summary_2025-12.md` |
