## How to Use This Rule

**This rule applies when creating any summary report.**

**Agents should:**
1. Save all summary reports to `docs/_reports/summaries/`
2. Use naming format: `{type}_summary_{YYYY-MM-DD}.md`
3. Follow the required template structure
4. Include accomplishments and upcoming work
5. Update the summary index README.md

**Trigger words:**
- "summarize", "summary", "create summary"
- "wrap up", "recap", "overview" (in summary context)
- End of sprint/phase/session

---

*This rule ensures consistent, discoverable summary reports that effectively communicate progress and status.*
